<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Lyft Inc. issued a massive correction to its o=
utlook for earnings margin in 2024, saying its margin is expected to expand=
 by 50 basis points =E2=80=94 not the 500 basis points written into an earn=
ings presentation released earlier on Tuesday.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThis is actually a correction from th=
e press release,=E2=80=9D Erin Brewer, Lyft=E2=80=99s chief financial offic=
er, said in a call with analysts. =E2=80=9CIn my prepared remarks, I refere=
nced 50 basis points of margin expansion.=E2=80=9D A spokesperson for the c=
ompany attributed the correction to a clerical error.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The blowout forecast may have contributed to a=
 surge in Lyft=E2=80=99s shares in after-market trading on Tuesday. The sto=
ck jumped as much as 67% on the company=E2=80=99s outlooks before erasing g=
ains during the call with investors. It was up 20% at 5:52 p.m. in New York=
.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here=E2=80=99s the <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34349750.258392/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9Bc=
mNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE3NTk1MDkvMDAwMTc1OTUwOTI0MDAwMDExL2x5ZnQtMjAyM3gx=
