toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">earni=
ngs release</a>, predicting =E2=80=9CAdjusted EBITDA margin expansion (calc=
ulated as a percentage of Gross Bookings) of approximately 500 basis points=
 year-over-year=E2=80=9D in 2024. That=C2=A0500 was supposed to be 50. Ah w=
ell.=C2=A0</p>
