<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The players who win the Super Bowl tr=
aditionally dump Gatorade on their coach. This is televised, and there is a=
n annual betting market on the color of the Gatorade. =E2=80=9CSuspicious b=
